data.description: Price Reduction Alert!!! Seller is offering $8k for buy down or improvements, you decide! This home is ready to kick back and relax with your friends! The possibilities are endless, 2nd home, or make it a private getaway home! Home features a huge detached RV/car garage shop with hookups for 2 RV's and onsite dump stations. Home is set up and ready for you! Inside the home you will be greeted by a generous sized kitchen with eating space, and huge living room with a woodstove to keep warm on those chilly Ocean Shores nights! Primary bedroom is on the main floor with its own bathroom. 1/2 bath with utility room is also located on the main floor, makes it convenient for guest. upstairs you will find a 2nd bedroom and huge loft, den/off.
